Interface IRelationshipElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IClass, IHasDataSpecification, IHasExtensions, IHasSemantics, IQualifiable, IReferable, ISubmodelElement

    public interface IRelationshipElement
extends ISubmodelElement
    A relationship element is used to define a relationship between two elements being either referable (model reference) or external (global reference).
